[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0592","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0592.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0361","title":"LaserFiche NetWare 版敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"LaserFiche for NetWare 版本以明文形式存储用户名和密码，导致邻近网络的攻击者可通过访问系统文件获取管理员凭证，造成敏感信息泄露。同时，系统允许管理员配置更改但未记录日志，使得未授权操作无法追溯审计。攻击者可利用窃取的凭证对系统进行进一步未授权访问与控制。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0361"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.863","remediation":"升级到 LaserFiche 现代版本（如 9.0 以上）以使用加密存储和审计日志功能；若无法升级，迁移至 Hyland 或其他具备加密存储与操作审计的文档管理平台。作为临时缓解措施，在网络层限制对 LaserFiche 服务的访问来源，仅允许受信任管理 IP 连接，并在 NetWare 服务器上启用文件系统和操作审计日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0361","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0361.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0361","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0361.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0361.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7ch8-6pch-qhqg/GHSA-7ch8-6pch-qhqg.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0361.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82496/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000420.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--106f99f3-e05b-4e49-be82-91767e97aac7.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0592.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0598","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0598.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0364","title":"Microsoft Access 97 数据库密码明文存储漏洞","description":"Microsoft Access 97 存在数据库密码明文存储漏洞，该软件在创建受密码保护的数据库时，将用户设置的数据库密码以未经加密的明文形式写入外部的 MDB 文件头部区域。本地攻击者通过文本编辑器或十六进制查看工具直接打开该 MDB 文件即可从文件二进制数据中提取完整的数据库密码，从而绕过身份验证机制完全访问受保护的数据库内容。该漏洞源于 Access 97 在设计时未对存储的密码进行加密处理，影响 Microsoft Access 97 所有版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。建议用户升级至更高版本 Microsoft Office 或使用第三方加密工具对数据库文件进行额外保护。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0364"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.247","remediation":"Microsoft Access 97 已停止支持多年，建议立即迁移至受支持的 Microsoft 365 或 Office 2021 等现代版本。如暂时无法迁移，避免在共享网络位置存放含密码的 .mdb 文件，并使用 Windows EFS 或 BitLocker 对数据库文件所在目录进行加密，同时将数据库密码替换为 Windows 集成身份验证。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91816470220259&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0364.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0364","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0364.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0364.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hvp5-q7xm-fj7p/GHSA-hvp5-q7xm-fj7p.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0364.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--80c82ddc-bc10-4574-98b0-fe5e3ff3aadf.json","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/windows.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0598.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0622","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0622.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0388","title":"DataLynx suGuard 1.0 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"DataLynx suGuard 1.0 存在本地权限提升漏洞。该程序在执行 ps 命令时信任 PATH 环境变量，未对程序路径进行绝对路径引用，导致本地攻击者可通过修改 PATH 环境变量将恶意程序替换为 ps，从而以 root 权限执行任意命令。攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，利用难度较低，危害较高。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0388"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:17.403","remediation":"将 suGuard 中对 ps 命令的调用路径从相对路径改为绝对路径（如 /bin/ps 或 /usr/bin/ps），或在执行前将 PATH 环境变量重置为安全值（如 /bin:/usr/bin），防止攻击者通过篡改 PATH 劫持命令执行。建议立即停止使用已停止维护的 DataLynx suGuard，迁移到持续更新的替代方案（如 sudo 或 doas）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/3186","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19146","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0388.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0388","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0388.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0388.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-ggpc-mwvf-qx65/GHSA-ggpc-mwvf-qx65.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-0388.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--1c737c62-180c-407a-8f21-cd64a33a52c3.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0622.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0630","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0630.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0393","title":"Eric Allman Sendmail 头扫描拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sendmail 8.8.x 及 8.9.2 版本在处理邮件头时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标邮件服务器发送包含大量邮件头的特制邮件消息，触发 Sendmail 的邮件头预扫描（headers prescan）过程消耗过度资源，导致服务崩溃或无法响应正常请求，造成拒绝服务。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0393"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:18.040","remediation":"升级至 Sendmail 8.9.3 或更高版本，该版本修复了 headers prescan 处理逻辑中的缺陷。若无法升级，可在 sendmail.cf 中限制每个邮件的最大头部数量（MaxHeadersLength 参数），并在 MTA 层面配置 rate limiting 限制单连接请求频率以缓解 DoS 攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91694391227372&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/23167","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0393.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0393","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0393.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0393.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-34q2-7xrv-pfcm/GHSA-34q2-7xrv-pfcm.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/sendmail_parsing_redirection.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0393.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0630.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0632","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0632.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0394","title":"DPEC Courseware Web Server 任意用户密码修改漏洞","description":"DPEC Courseware Web Server 存在密码修改漏洞，远程攻击者可在无需知道原始密码的情况下，直接修改其他用户的账户密码。该漏洞影响 DPEC Online Courseware 系统，攻击者利用此漏洞可获取其他用户的账户控制权，进而访问课程资料或执行未授权操作。由于无需身份认证即可利用，危害等级严重，CVSS 评分 10.0。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0394"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:18.173","remediation":"立即停用 DPEC Online Courseware 并迁移至其他受支持的在线课程平台；如无法立即替换，应在 Web 服务器层面通过 ACL 限制管理后台访问 IP 范围，并禁用密码修改功能涉及的 CGI 脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91651770630788&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6df16fc0c02ccadd2d0fbb0029e3db345d75f1c8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0394.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0394","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0394.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ec31d5593e31331ed2058e001803e087d65aa416/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0394.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2wqv-jwmj-rrvv/GHSA-2wqv-jwmj-rrvv.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0394.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/565/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000425.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a621bf71-a318-4813-9d54-b3d23b540b4c.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0632.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0632.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0632.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0635","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0635.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0397","title":"Quakenbush NT密码评估器 网络明文传输密码漏洞","description":"Quakenbush NT 密码评估器（NT Password Appraiser）的演示版存在敏感信息泄露漏洞，该软件在评估密码强度时，将用户密码以明文形式通过网络传输，导致攻击者可通过网络嗅探方式截获目标系统的用户凭据。该漏洞影响 Quakenbush NT Password Appraiser 演示版，攻击者只需与目标处于同一网络段即可实施嗅探攻击，获取的密码可用于后续系统未授权访问。CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0397"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:18.550","remediation":"立即停止使用 Quakenbush NT Password Appraiser 演示版，改用完整版或其他密码评估工具（如 John the Ripper、ophcrack）。如必须使用该工具，请确保在网络层启用加密（如 IPsec 或 VPN）以防止密码明文传输。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0397","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/af5cedcf472f3690d94c4249ff35246f15692534/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0397.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0397","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0397.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ec31d5593e31331ed2058e001803e087d65aa416/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0397.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9qgw-6p53-x34x/GHSA-9qgw-6p53-x34x.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0397.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82470/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000426.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5d314605-9006-4ec7-ad70-4a7c6fdfbca2.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0635.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0637","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0637.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0398","title":"SSH Communications Security SSH 服务器过期帐户认证绕过漏洞","description":"tags.<value>SSH 1.2.27 和 2.0.11 版本在 Linux 系统中存在身份认证绕过漏洞，已过期的用户账户仍可通过 SSH 服务正常登录系统。攻击者可利用该漏洞通过已过期账户获取系统未授权访问权限，可能导致敏感信息泄露或进一步攻击。该漏洞影响运行上述 SSH 版本的 Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议升级到不受影响的 SSH 版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0398"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:18.677","remediation":"立即升级到 OpenSSH 3.0p1 及以上版本，或升级到 SSH 2.3.0 及以上版本。旧版 SSH 1.x/2.0.x 存在多项已知漏洞且已停止维护。如无法升级，可在 SSH 服务端配置文件 /etc/ssh/sshd_config 中设置 PermitEmptyPasswords no 和 UsePAM yes，启用 PAM 认证以强制检查账户过期状态。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0398"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0637.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0683","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0683.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0448","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 日志请求方法绕过漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 及 Apache 等 Web 服务器在记录 HTTP 请求日志时，未对请求方法（Method）字段长度进行有效限制，远程攻击者可通过构造超长 HTTP 请求方法字符串，将实际请求的恶意 URL 隐藏在日志记录之外，从而实现日志绕过。该漏洞允许攻击者在未授权情况下隐藏攻击痕迹，影响运行 IIS 4.0 的 Windows NT 系统，增加安全审计和溯源难度。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0448"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:25.087","remediation":"升级至 Windows 2000 自带的 IIS 5.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复日志绕过问题。如无法升级，可启用 IIS 日志记录中的 URI 查询字段截断功能，并限制 HTTP 请求方法长度不超过 1024 字节以缓解攻击。Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议尽快迁移至受支持的操作系统版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0448","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19149","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/727cf5277c8c23eaf8725829e26aff2ea619a86c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0448.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0448","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0448.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/77fd3cf167afc5c82646a191836bcd2f9e51b459/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0448.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2mhj-64gr-7wf9/GHSA-2mhj-64gr-7wf9.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0448.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0448.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000429.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0683.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0683.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0683.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0692","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0692.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0452","title":"OpenSource Application 后门密码漏洞","description":"某开源应用程序的开发者在代码中预留了后门密码，导致未经授权的远程攻击者可通过该预设密码直接登录系统或访问敏感功能，完全绕过正常认证机制。该漏洞影响多个开源应用版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。受影响的系统管理员应检查并更换所有默认凭据，同时更新至已移除后门的版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0452"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:25.590","remediation":"立即审查受影响应用的源代码，移除所有硬编码的后门账号和密码；修改所有默认凭据为强密码；更新到已修复此问题的官方最新版本；如无法升级，在应用层和网络层同时实施访问控制，限制对受影响服务的访问来源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0452","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1231f6f5f21cc87f3264c90adadd01cbb12e76ba/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0452.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0452","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0452.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/77fd3cf167afc5c82646a191836bcd2f9e51b459/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0452.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q2g5-95p7-cx94/GHSA-q2g5-95p7-cx94.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0452.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/F/ftp_backdoor.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0692.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0693","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0693.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0453","title":"Cisco CDP 设备信息泄露漏洞","description":"Cisco 设备上的发现协议（CDP）存在信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标设备的 1999 端口发送 SYN 数据包来识别 Cisco 设备的存在及类型。该漏洞允许攻击者获取设备信息，为进一步攻击提供侦察基础，影响大量 Cisco 路由器、交换机等网络设备。攻击无需认证，仅需网络可达即可实施，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0453"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:25.710","remediation":"在不需要 Cisco Discovery Protocol (CDP) 的接口上执行 `no cdp enable` 命令禁用 CDP，或在全局模式下执行 `no cdp run` 完全关闭 CDP 服务。在网络边界防火墙或 ACL 中过滤目标端口 1999 的入站 SYN 包，阻止外部扫描识别设备型号。升级到较新版本的 Cisco IOS 以获取 CDP 安全增强特性。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0453","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1231f6f5f21cc87f3264c90adadd01cbb12e76ba/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0453.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0453","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0453.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/77fd3cf167afc5c82646a191836bcd2f9e51b459/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0453.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x3m2-cfrc-7vhc/GHSA-x3m2-cfrc-7vhc.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0453.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000430.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/NVDFeatureAnalysis/blob/493a57a415cc110f9945148abd717eeb92f6ca7e/originalDataset/cveIDThreatType/cve_idinfor"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0693.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0694","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0694.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0454","title":"多款操作系统 TCP/IP 协议栈远程操作系统识别漏洞","description":"远程攻击者可通过向目标主机发送特制的 IP 或 ICMP 数据包，根据目标系统对异常数据包的不同响应特征（如 TTL 值、DF 标志位、ICMP 错误消息格式等）来识别其操作系统类型。该漏洞利用不同操作系统 TCP/IP 协议栈实现的差异进行被动或主动指纹识别，攻击者无需任何身份认证即可远程执行。使用 nmap、queso 等工具可自动化完成此探测过程，为后续针对性攻击提供信息支撑。该漏洞影响多种开源路由器及通用操作系统，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0454"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:25.877","remediation":"在边界防火墙上配置 ACL 规则丢弃不必要的 ICMP 报文（如 timestamp request、address mask request），并限制 TTL 回复行为；升级操作系统至最新版本，现代系统默认已缓解此类指纹识别攻击；使用 TCP 栈参数调优（如修改初始 TTL 值、禁用 ICMP 重定向）增加识别难度。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2048","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0454.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1231f6f5f21cc87f3264c90adadd01cbb12e76ba/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0454.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0454","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/77fd3cf167afc5c82646a191836bcd2f9e51b459/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0454.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0454.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h9fp-2pjq-92gw/GHSA-h9fp-2pjq-92gw.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0454.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82856/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0694.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0720","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0720.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0465","title":"Lynx 和 Microsoft Internet Explorer IMG 标签宽参数远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"远程攻击者可通过在网页中嵌入包含超大 width 参数的 IMG 标签，诱使目标用户使用 Lynx 或 Internet Explorer 浏览器访问该页面，触发浏览器在处理畸形 HTML 元素时的拒绝服务漏洞，导致浏览器崩溃。该漏洞影响 Lynx 及早期 Internet Explorer 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可实施攻击，危害等级高危。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0465"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:27.187","remediation":"升级 Lynx 至 2.8.1 以上版本可修复此漏洞；Internet Explorer 用户应升级至 IE 5.01 以上版本。当前建议弃用已停止支持的 IE，改用 Microsoft Edge 或 Chrome 等现代浏览器，并在 Web 应用中严格校验用户提交的 HTML IMG 标签 width 参数，限制其最大值防止拒绝服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0465","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0465.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0465","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0465.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0465.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3prc-hp8x-jp9c/GHSA-3prc-hp8x-jp9c.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0465.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82826/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0465.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0720.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0720.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0746","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0746.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0495","title":"Microsoft Windows SMB 目录遍历漏洞","description":"SMB（Server Message Block）协议共享中存在路径遍历漏洞。由于服务端在处理SMB共享访问请求时未对\"..\"（点点）目录跳转序列进行充分过滤和校验，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过在SMB共享路径中构造包含\"../\"的目录遍历序列，突破共享根目录限制，访问目标文件系统中的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响范围广泛，CVSS v2.0评分为10.0，危害等级严重，攻击者无需认证即可通过网络远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0495"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:31.207","remediation":"升级 Samba 至 2.0.6 或更高版本，该版本修复了 SMB 共享中路径遍历（..）导致文件系统越权访问的问题。如无法升级，在 smb.conf 中为每个共享设置 `valid users` 限制访问用户，并使用 `wide links = no` 和 `follow symlinks = no` 禁用符号链接跟随作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/837"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0746.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0748","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0748.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0497","title":"FTP服务 匿名登录配置不当漏洞","description":"FTP 服务器启用了匿名登录功能，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可使用 anonymous 或 ftp 账号连接目标 FTP 服务，导致服务器上的文件被任意读取、下载或上传。该漏洞允许未授权访问敏感数据，若结合写权限还可用于上传恶意文件。攻击条件仅需目标开放 21 端口且允许匿名登录，利用门槛极低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0497"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:31.483","remediation":"禁止匿名 FTP 登录：在 FTP 服务器配置中将 anonymous 用户禁用，或设置 /etc/ftpusers 文件禁止匿名访问；若业务需要保留匿名服务，应使用 chroot 限制文件系统访问范围、设置只读权限并启用日志审计；建议用 SFTP/FTPS 替代明文 FTP 协议。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0497","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0497.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/122439703ba8729c2a612b649ea87112305b8e28/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0497.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0497","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc69cd1e5221f68ef56bd10c5c61adf76a19f0fc/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0497.json","https://github.com/DefectDojo/django-DefectDojo/blob/d9905eb7656178d3e59e0bf8f1d53a9ee9e50186/unittests/scans/openvas/many_vuln.xml","https://github.com/0xMarcio/cve/blob/a5ee56580623b0ed40e39c2c083edd8b799653e9/1999/CVE-1999-0497.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q5hp-pm99-c5x6/GHSA-q5hp-pm99-c5x6.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/ftp_anonymous.nasl","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/2018/gb_ftp_anonymous_detect.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0748.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0769","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0769.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0515","title":"Unix /etc/hosts.equiv 未授权主机信任关系提权漏洞","description":"Unix 系统通过 /etc/hosts.equiv 与 ~/.rhosts 文件配置基于主机的信任关系，实现无密码远程登录。当该文件中被配置为不受限制的信任项（例如包含单独的\"+\"符号）时，系统将允许来自任意主机的任意用户以本地任意用户身份登录，从而绕过身份认证。攻击者在可访问目标主机网络的条件下，利用 rlogin、rsh 等基于 rhosts 的远程服务，无需提供凭据即可获得目标系统的同等权限，可能造成权限提升与未授权访问，影响范围涵盖所有启用此类信任配置的 Unix/Linux 系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0515"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:33.550","remediation":"立即编辑 /etc/hosts.equiv 与每个用户的 ~/.rhosts，删除其中单独的「+」号及「+ +」等无限制信任条目，仅保留明确的主机名与用户名；停止并禁用 rsh、rlogin、rexec 等基于信任的 R 服务（如执行 chkconfig rsh off），改用 SSH 并配置基于密钥的认证；在主机防火墙限制 512/513/514 端口仅允许内网可信地址访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0515","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/10323cb4135457b41074412d623aa2116c4e1200/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0515.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0515","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0515.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4efc2590fd3e232024591793a186ed6577aaac2a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0515.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdec8f567bb266b7b6813bda45223a258023f538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jmw9-2v63-7gm2/GHSA-jmw9-2v63-7gm2.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0515.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000432.txt","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0515.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0769.toml"}]